---
import { CloudRain } from "lucide-astro";
---

<div
  class="grid grid-cols-1 items-start gap-6 sm:grid-cols-[repeat(2,minmax(0,13rem))] lg:grid-cols-[repeat(4,14.5rem)] lg:auto-rows-[14.5rem]"
>
  <article
    class="relative aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-4xl bg-[#d8d8d8] sm:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full"
    aria-labelledby="awaodori-title"
  >
    <h2
      id="awaodori-title"
      class="absolute bottom-7 left-7 rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base font-bold leading-none text-black shadow-sm"
    >
      Awaodori 🕺
    </h2>
  </article>

  <article
    class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-4xl bg-white p-6 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-1"
    aria-labelledby="weather-title"
  >
    <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
      <div
        class="grid size-20 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full bg-[#d8d8d8] text-sm font-bold text-black"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        気温アイコン
      </div>
      <div
        class="min-w-0 flex-1 rounded-sm bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,#82a4b6_0%,#3f7ca3_100%)] p-2 text-white"
        aria-hidden="true"
      >
        <p class="text-xs font-bold leading-none">徳島市</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-normal leading-none">19°</p>
        <CloudRain class="mt-3 size-4" strokeWidth={2.5} />
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs font-bold leading-tight">にわか雨</p>
        <p class="text-xs font-bold leading-tight">最高:22° 最低:19°</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 id="weather-title" class="text-sm font-bold leading-tight text-black">
      徳島の気温ウィジェット
    </h2>
  </article>

  <article
    class="flex aspect-square flex-col justify-between rounded-4xl bg-white p-6 lg:col-start-4 lg:row-start-1"
    aria-labelledby="yakimochi-title"
  >
    <div class="size-20 rounded-full bg-[#d8d8d8]" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    <div>
      <h2
        id="yakimochi-title"
        class="text-xl font-bold leading-tight text-black"
      >
        滝のやきもち
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-medium leading-tight text-black">
        美味しい和菓子なので、焼き立てを食べることをおすすめします。
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article
    class="rounded-4xl bg-white p-8 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-3 lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full"
    aria-labelledby="tokushima-about-title"
  >
    <h2
      id="tokushima-about-title"
      class="text-base font-normal leading-tight text-black"
    >
      I live in
      <span class="ml-1 font-serif-display text-2xl font-bold">
        Tokushima.
      </span>
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-medium leading-relaxed text-[#8c8e8d]">
      正直にいうと徳島は何もないです。でも住みやすい場所ではあると思います。そんな徳島のごくわずかなスポットを集めました。ここに載せていないものだと、お遍路や鳴門の渦潮なんかもありますね。一度訪れてみてください。
    </p>
  </article>

  <article
    class="relative aspect-square overflow-hidden rounded-4xl bg-[#d8d8d8] sm:col-span-2 lg:col-start-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-2 lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full"
    aria-labelledby="museum-title"
  >
    <h2
      id="museum-title"
      class="absolute bottom-7 left-7 rounded-xl bg-white px-4 py-3 text-base font-bold leading-none text-black shadow-sm"
    >
      大塚国際美術館
    </h2>
  </article>
</div>
